{{c|tmux-mem-cpu-load}} is a small program designed to monitor system activity in the status line of {{c|tmux}}. [[Tmux/plugins/tmux-mem-cpu-load|See the {{c|tmux-mem-cpu-load}} sub-article]] for more details on the installation process.

